required.name: Belarus
required.note:
Visas are issued on arrival at the Minsk International Airport
if the support documents were submitted not later than 3 business days before expected date of arrival.

required.name: Bhutan
required.note: Visa approved via tour operators only

required.name: Brazil
required.note: Tourist visa is issued for a maximum stay of 90 days.

required.name: Central African Republic
required.note: Visa can be issued at the Consulate General of France.

required.name: China
required.note:
72-hours visa free visit when in transit at Beijing, Chengdu, Chongqing, Dalian, Guangzhou, Guilin, Shenyang, Xi'an, Nanjing and Wuhan.
144-hours (6 days) visa free transit in Shanghai, Jiangsu and Zhejiang.

required.name: Democratic Republic of the Congo
required.note: Visa not required for Congolese-born visitors

required.name: Nauru
required.note: Criminal record and medical fitness certificates are not required for Australian citizens.

required.name: Nigeria
required.note: Visa not required for Nigerian-born citizens

required.name: Pakistan
required.note: Visa on arrival when travelling on business valid for 30 days. Conditions apply.

required.name: Sudan
required.note: Visa not required for Sudanese-born citizens

required.name: Uzbekistan
required.note: Pre-arranged visa can be obtained on arrival for a maximum of 7 days.

required.name: Vietnam
required.note:
Pre-arranged visa obtained online through travel agencies available at Hanoi, Ho Chi Minh City or Da Nang airports.
Phú Quốc without a visa for up to 30 days.

not-required.name: Argentina

not-required.note: 90 days within any 180 day period in the Schengen area

not-required.name: Chile
not-required.note: 90 days. Australian tourists entering Chile through Santiago International Airport are required to pay a “reciprocity fee” of US$117.

evisa.name: Ivory Coast
evisa.note: 3 months; eVisa holders must arrive via Port Bouet Airport.

evisa.name: Gabon
evisa.note: Electronic visa holders must arrive via Libreville International Airport.

evisa.name: Myanmar
evisa.note: 28 days. eVisa holders must arrive via Yangon, Nay Pyi Taw or Mandalay airports.

evisa.name: Turkey
evisa.note: 3 months. Cruise ship passengers do not require a visa for up to 72 hours. eVisa can be obtained on arrival for a higher fee.

on-arrival.name: Armenia
on-arrival.note: 120 days. Obtainable on arrival at Zvartnots International Airport or prior to travel online.

on-arrival.name: Bangladesh
on-arrival.note: 30 days. Not available at all entry points.

on-arrival.name: Cambodia
on-arrival.note: 30 days. Visa is also obtainable online.

on-arrival.name: Cape Verde
on-arrival.note: Not available at all entry points.

on-arrival.name: Djibouti
on-arrival.note: Not available at all entry points.

on-arrival.name: Ethiopia
on-arrival.note: Not available at all entry points.

on-arrival.name: Jordan
on-arrival.note: Conditions apply. Not available at all entry points.

on-arrival.name: Laos
on-arrival.note: 30 days. Not available at all entry points.

on-arrival.name: Lebanon
on-arrival.note: 1 month extendable for 2 additional months; granted free of charge at Beirut International Airport or any other port of entry if there is no Israeli visa or seal, holding a telephone number, an address in Lebanon, and a non refundable return or circle trip ticket.

on-arrival.name: Papua New Guinea
on-arrival.note: 30 days, available at Gurney Airport (Alotau), Mount Hagen Airport, Port Moresby Airport and Tokua Airport (Rabaul).

on-arrival.name: Paraguay
on-arrival.note: 90 days, only available at Silvio Pettirossi International Airport in Luque. Reciprocity fee applies.

on-arrival.name: Qatar
on-arrival.note: 1 month. Not available at all entry points.

on-arrival.name: Somalia
on-arrival.note:
30 days, provided an invitation letter issued by the sponsor has been submitted
to the Airport Immigration Department at least 2 days before arrival.

on-arrival.name: Tajikistan
on-arrival.note: 45 days at Dushanbe International Airport. Visa also available online. E-visa holders can enter through all border points.

on-arrival.name: East Timor
on-arrival.note: 30 days. Not available at all entry points.

on-arrival.name: Uganda
on-arrival.note: Determined at the port of entry. May apply online.

on-arrival.name: Ukraine
on-arrival.note: Visa on arrival valid for 15 days is available only at the Boryspil International Airport. Invitation letter is not required for Australian citizens.

on-arrival.name: Zambia
on-arrival.note: 90 days; also eligible for a universal visa allowing access to Zimbabwe. eVisa available.

on-arrival.name: Zimbabwe
on-arrival.note: 3 months. Strictly tourism purposes only. Also eligible for a universal visa allowing access to Zambia. eVisa available.
